    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i tried the pressure but the cut is pretty wide, like i can almost see the fatty tissue underneath. do u think the honey paste will be enough to close it up or keep it from gaping open? i'm just worried if i go to the doc they'll charge me a lot for stitches when the honey might work just as well.",
